Package neureka.calculus.environment

Interface OperationTypeImplementation<FinalType>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractOperationTypeImplementation, Activation, Broadcast, Convolution, GenericImplementation, Operator, Scalarization
    public interface OperationTypeImplementation<FinalType>
    This class is the middle layer of the 3 tier abstraction architecture of Neureka's operation implementations. Conceptually an implementation of this interface represents "a way of execution" for the OperationType to which an instance of said implementation would belong. The "+" operator for example has different OperationTypeImplementation instances for different ExecutionCall instances. Tensors within an execution call having the same shape would trigger the Operation instance of the OperationType, whereas otherwise the Convolution or Broadcast implementation might be called.
